{"timestamp": "2026-05-21T00:59:14.481579+00:00", "target_file": "2023 Reflection (highlights)", "operation": "Concept Indexing", "prompt_tokens": 3006, "completion_tokens": 3246, "total_tokens": 6252, "prompt": "Analyze this Logseq outliner page. Extract semantic connections AND propose safe per-block lint corrections.\nReturn structured JSON only.\n\nPage title: 2023 Reflection (highlights)\n\nBlocks available for semantic_corrections:\n(no blocks with id:: found — omit semantic_corrections)\n\nFull page content:\ntitle:: 2023 Reflection (highlights)\nauthor:: [[Bullet Journal]]\nfull-title:: \"2023 Reflection\"\ncategory:: #articles\nurl:: https://bulletjournal.com/blogs/bulletjournalist/2023-reflection?utm_source=Klaviyo&utm_medium=campaign&utm_term=campaign&em_source=klaviyo&_kx=zc5gasWuG2dyts75z-Z3a8BBpN6bpq10xGD_MJ7dDHtE7dCxRaSls2EkjZIsq82E.N4sebt\nsummary:: In his yearly reflection for 2023, the founder of Bullet Journal, Ryder Carroll, shares his personal and professional insights. He discusses the growth of the company, transitioning from a business to a company with a larger team. He also mentions the launch of BuJo U, a platform for the Bullet Journal community, and the development of a certification program for Bullet Journal trainers. Carroll reflects on the impact of his work and his commitment to ongoing education. He shares his personal highlights from the year, including attending workshops and a silent retreat. Overall, Carroll emphasizes the importance of growth, learning, and making an impact in both personal and professional spheres.\ntags:: #[[bullet journal]] \n![](http://bulletjournal.com/cdn/shop/articles/Moon_600x.jpg?v=1705703654)\n- Highlights first synced by [[Readwise]] [[Tue, 24-12-2024]]\n  type:: risorsa\n  status:: active\n\t- **Impact**\n\t  \n\t  When I launched [bulletjournal.com](http://bulletjournal.com) in 2013, it never occurred to me to turn it into a business. It being free was kind of the whole idea. It was to give back to others who shared their knowledge for free online. That was until I learned something that changed my mind:\n\t  \n\t  > Businesses can be force multipliers for supporting anything you care about.\n\t  \n\t  This moved me to a new space of creating a mission-driven company that is sustainable while being able to make an impact in a variety of ways.\n\t  \n\t  For example, I donate 10% of my income to charitable organizations. Bullet Journal, the company, donates 10% of its profits, which is a lot more than my contribution as an individual. This year we were able to provide hundreds of scholarships, and make our most sizable contribution yet to our charitable organization of choice: [Giving What We Can](http://givingwhatwecan.org). In a world with subjective business metrics, this felt like an objective measure of success. ([View Highlight](https://read.readwise.io/read/01hmnadw3hpp3jkk64at1hbyze))\n### Matryca MARPA Validation\n- assigned-domain:: risorsa\n- detected-tags:: #articles #bullet journal\n- bipartite-violations::\n  - direct_entity_link:Bullet Journal<->bullet journal (missing contains::/leads_to::/expresses::)\n  - direct_entity_link:Bullet Journal<->Readwise (missing contains::/leads_to::/expresses::)\n  - direct_entity_link:Bullet Journal<->Tue, 24-12-2024 (missing contains::/leads_to::/expresses::)\n  - direct_entity_link:bullet journal<->Readwise (missing contains::/leads_to::/expresses::)\n  - direct_entity_link:bullet journal<->Tue, 24-12-2024 (missing contains::/leads_to::/expresses::)\n  - direct_entity_link:Readwise<->Tue, 24-12-2024 (missing contains::/leads_to::/expresses::)\n  - direct_entity_link:Bullet Journal<->bullet journal (missing contains::/leads_to::/expresses::)\n  - direct_entity_link:Bullet Journal<->Readwise (missing contains::/leads_to::/expresses::)\n  - direct_entity_link:Bullet Journal<->Tue, 24-12-2024 (missing contains::/leads_to::/expresses::)\n  - direct_entity_link:bullet journal<->Readwise (missing contains::/leads_to::/expresses::)\n  - direct_entity_link:bullet journal<->Tue, 24-12-2024 (missing contains::/leads_to::/expresses::)\n  - direct_entity_link:Readwise<->Tue, 24-12-2024 (missing contains::/leads_to::/expresses::)\n", "response": "{\"summary\":\"Ryder Carroll's 2023 reflection on Bullet Journal growth, community impact, and charitable giving.\",\"cross_references\":[{\"concept\":\"Author\",\"relation\":\"authored_by\",\"target\":\"[[Bullet Journal]]\"},{\"concept\":\"Highlights\",\"relation\":\"synced_by\",\"target\":\"[[Readwise]]\"},{\"concept\":\"Charitable Organization\",\"relation\":\"donates_to\",\"target\":\"[[Giving What We Can]]\"},{\"concept\":\"Business Model Transition\",\"relation\":\"related_to\",\"target\":\"[[Mission-Driven Company]]\"}],\"suggested_tags\":[\"#reflection\",\"#business-growth\",\"#charity\",\"#education\",\"#bullet-journal\"],\"moc_pointers\":[\"[[2023 Reflections]]\",\"[[Bullet Journal Resources]]\"],\"semantic_corrections\":[]}", "latency_seconds": 732.2391, "model": "qwen2.5-coder-7b", "ok": true, "error": null}
